Dataset description:Life experience data is compiled by Gapimnder based on multiple sources mainly data from Institute of Health Metrics and Evaluation in their Global Burden Disease studies (GBD 2019), World Population Prospects 2019 and Gapminder-Life expexctancy v.7 which is based on 100 sources and compiled by Mattias Lindgre. The data is combined as follow:- For the period between 1970-2019, we use the data from IHME GBD 2019. To go back in time we have combined the IHME data with our historic data from V7 and adjusted the data for 80 years so that it meets IHME data for the first year it exists. From 2020 up to 2100 we have extended IHME series with UN forecasts. In this version , we capture the impact of covid19 on life expectancy for the year 2020. Based data from Eurostat, Aburto et al. in their research paper and Heuveline &
